#ROOMS
#8700
@@yNorthwind Traverse@@N~
The wind-scoured quarter of the northern oasis opens around cistern ribs stitched with @@lbright blue@@N banners.@@N
Wind drives @@yyellow@@N grit in low ribbons while @@bbrown@@N retaining walls keep the lane coherent despite branching footpaths.@@N
From this square, the northern sky holds a fierce @@lbright blue@@N vault, and every marker suggests traders once moved in disciplined columns.@@N
Fresh sandal tracks cross older hoof marks and vanish at the next bend.@@N
~
0 10
D1
The caravan line continues through a bright seam of blown sand.
~
